"as :guilabel:`Street`, :guilabel:`City`, :guilabel:`State`, "
"and :guilabel:`ZIP`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`कंपनी का नाम`, :guilabel:`टैक्स आईडी` (TIN), और :guilabel:`देश` भरें। "
"अगर चाहें, तो अतिरिक्त वैकल्पिक फ़ील्ड जैसे :guilabel:`Street`, :guilabel:`शहर`, "
":guilabel:`State`, और :guilabel:`ZIP` भरें।"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:154
msgid "The :guilabel:`Country` must be set to :guilabel:`Jordan`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`देश` :guilabel:`Jordan` पर सेट होना चाहिए।"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:155
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Company Name` must match the name that is registered with the "
"Income and Sales Tax Department (ISTD)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`कंपनी का नाम` उस नाम से मेल खाना चाहिए जो Income and Sales Tax "
