msgstr "Odoo के ज़रिए JoFotara को इनवॉइस भेजना"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:171
msgid ""
"Once the company has been :ref:`linked with JoFotara <localizations/jordan/"
